  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommitException
    used to show exceptions which have been raised during commit operations
    CompressionException
    used to show an error raised during compression process
    DataAccessException
    used to show an error raised during database access (can't reach the database)
    DatabaseConnectionException
    used to show an error raised during database connection (wrong information)
    DatabaseException
    used to show an error raised during database process (error in request)
    DecompressException
    used to show an error raised during decompress process
    ExportProjectException
    used to show an error raised during export process
    HashingException
    used to show exception that are possibly raised during the usage of the PasswordHasher class.
    InvalidDriverException
    used to show an error raised because the database drivers are missing or wrong
    ModifyUserDataException
    used to show an error raised during update of user's info
    ProjectDataAccessException
    used to show an error raised during accessing the project data or information : can't reach the project
    SignInException
    used to show an error raised during signing in a user
    SignUpException
    used to show an error raised during signing up a user
    ValueNotFoundException
    used to show an error raised because a value is missing
    VersioningException
    used to show exceptions which have been raised during versioning process
